unning   0          1h\nonap          dev-sdnc-portal-6db596bd95-cr9rs            1/1       Running   0          1h\nonap          dev-sdnc-ueb-listener-76b8cc8d7c-5vgr6      1/1       Running   0          1h\nonap          dev-zookeeper-b69c5bddf-8fx95               1/1       Running   0          1h",
